New Records: E Nsue scored a hat-trick in the Africa Cup of Nations Group A match between Equatorial Guinea and Guinea-Bissau
Key Match Events: E Nsue scored a hat-trick for Equatorial Guinea, J Miranda Boacho scored a goal for Equatorial Guinea, E Obiang Obono scored an own goal for Guinea-Bissau, and J Correia scored a goal for Guinea-Bissau in the 93rd minute
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match took place at the Stade Olympique Alassane Ouattara with an attendance of 13,888
